available_connectors.name: FRED速 API
available_connectors.description: The FRED速 API is a web service that allows developers to write programs and build applications that retrieve economic data from the FRED速 and ALFRED速 websites hosted by the Economic Research Division of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis. Requests can be customized according to data source, release, category, series, and other preferences.

available_apis.name: fred/category
available_apis.description: Get a category

available_apis.name: fred/category/children
available_apis.description: Get the child categories for a specified parent category

available_apis.name: fred/category/related
available_apis.description: Get the related categories for a category

available_apis.name: fred/category/series
available_apis.description: Get the series in a category

available_apis.name: fred/category/tags
available_apis.description: Get the tags for a category

available_apis.name: fred/category/related_tags
available_apis.description: Get the related tags for a category

available_apis.name: fred/releases
available_apis.description: Get all releases of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/releases/dates
available_apis.description: Get release dates for all releases of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/release
available_apis.description: Get a release of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/release/dates
available_apis.description: Get release dates for a release of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/release/series
available_apis.description: Get the series on a release of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/release/sources
available_apis.description: Get the sources for a release of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/release/tags
available_apis.description: Get the tags for a release

available_apis.name: fred/release/related_tags
available_apis.description: Get the related tags for a release

available_apis.name: fred/release/tables
available_apis.description: Get the release tables for a given release

available_apis.name: fred/sources
available_apis.description: Get all sources of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/source
available_apis.description: Get a source of economic data

available_apis.name: fred/source/releases
available_apis.description: Get the releases for a source

available_apis.name: fred/tags
available_apis.description: Get all tags, search for tags, or get tags by name

available_apis.name: fred/related_tags
available_apis.description: Get the related tags for one or more tags

available_apis.name: fred/tags/series
available_apis.description: Get the series matching tags
